npm init
npm install express mongoose cors dotenv nodemon

expres:- lightweight and fast webframework for nodejs
mongoose:- it makes interacting with mongodb through nodejs makes simpler
cors:- Cross version resource sharing, with this we can easily access something outside of server into our server
dotenv:- which loads env variables from .env file into process.env, this makes development simpler.
nodemon:- nodemon is a utility, that will monitor for any chages in you source code and automatically restart your server at the point when chages made in source code